MP3::M3U::Parser version 1.0
===========================

Parses M3U mp3 playlists and exports the parsed data to 
formats like xml and html.

Read the module's POD for documentation and examples.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make install

or under Windows:

   perl Makefile.PL
   nmake
   nmake install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules:

	File::Spec
	IO::File
	Data::Dumper

All are available on CPAN and standard in Perl 5.8.

